<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥١١٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">غُنْدَرٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6543">أَبِي جَمْرَةَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنَ عَبَّاسٍ</a> <span class="c2">«سُئِلَ عَنْ مُتْعَةِ النِّسَاءِ فَرَخَّصَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ لَهُ مَوْلًى لَهُ:</span> إِنَّمَا ذَلِكَ فِي الْحَالِ الشَّدِيدِ وَفِي النِّسَاءِ قِلَّةٌ أَوْ نَحْوَهُ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> نَعَمْ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>